# FitTrack Dev Handoff
## Dashboard Tab - Final Specification

---

# ğŸ¥‡ Component Breakdown with States

## 1. Header

**Component Name:** `Header`

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| date | Date | Yes | Current date to display |

**States:**
| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Default | Shows formatted date (e.g., "Wednesday, Dec 25") |

**Notes:**
- Date format: `weekday long, month short, day numeric`
- No loading/error states needed (always has data)

---

## 2. CycleBadge

**Component Name:** `CycleBadge`

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| phase | `'menstrual' \| 'follicular' \| 'ovulation' \| 'luteal'` | Yes | Current cycle phase |
| day | number | Yes | Day within current phase |

**States:**
| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Default | Shows pill with droplet icon + "Phase Â· Day X" |
| Empty/Not Set | Hide component entirely (don't show placeholder) |

**Notes:**
- Capitalize phase name in display
- Icon: Lucide `Droplet`, filled

---

## 3. CalorieCard

**Component Name:** `CalorieCard`

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| consumed | number | Yes | Calories consumed today |
| goal | number | Yes | Daily calorie goal |

**Computed:**
- `remaining = goal - consumed`
- `percentage = (consumed / goal) * 100` (cap at 100)

**States:**
| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Loading | Show skeleton: gray bar (animated pulse) where number would be |
| Empty | Show "0" for consumed, full goal, "X left" shows full goal |
| Has Data | Show consumed / goal, remaining, progress bar |
| Over Goal | Show consumed (no cap), remaining shows "0 left" or "X over" (decide with PM), bar fills 100% |
| Error | Show "Unable to load" with retry button |

**Notes:**
- Format numbers with commas: `1,450` not `1450`
- Progress bar: solid fill, no gradient
- "X left" uses accent color

---

## 4. MacroCard

**Component Name:** `MacroCard`

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| protein | { current: number, goal: number } | Yes | Protein data |
| carbs | { current: number, goal: number } | Yes | Carbs data |
| fat | { current: number, goal: number } | Yes | Fat data |

**States:**
| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Loading | Show 3 skeleton rows with pulsing bars |
| Empty | Show 0 / goal for each macro |
| Has Data | Show current / goal with gradient progress bars |
| Partial Data | Show available macros, 0 for missing |
| Error | Show "Unable to load" with retry button |

**Notes:**
- All three bars use same gradient (Lâ†’R: `gradientStart` â†’ `gradientEnd`)
- Each macro is a `MacroRow` subcomponent

---

## 5. MacroRow (subcomponent)

**Component Name:** `MacroRow`

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| name | string | Yes | "Protein", "Carbs", or "Fat" |
| current | number | Yes | Grams consumed |
| goal | number | Yes | Goal in grams |

**States:**
| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Default | Label left, "X / Yg" right, gradient bar below |

---

## 6. StepsCard

**Component Name:** `StepsCard`

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| steps | number | Yes | Steps taken today |
| goal | number | Yes | Daily step goal |

**States:**
| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Loading | Show empty ring with pulsing center |
| Empty | Show "0" in center, empty ring |
| Has Data | Show "X.Xk" in center, ring fills proportionally |
| Goal Met | Ring at 100%, optionally show celebration state |
| Error | Show "â€”" in center, empty ring |

**Notes:**
- Display as "X.Xk" (e.g., "6.2k" not "6,234")
- Ring has square ends (`strokeLinecap: butt`)
- Gradient applied to ring stroke

---

## 7. SleepCard

**Component Name:** `SleepCard`

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| hours | number | Yes | Hours slept last night |
| goal | number | Yes | Sleep goal in hours |

**States:**
| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Loading | Show skeleton number |
| Empty/Not Logged | Show "â€”" with "not logged" subtext |
| Has Data | Show "X.X / Yh" with "last night" subtext |
| Error | Show "â€”" |

**Notes:**
- No progress bar â€” number display only
- This is informational (not updated throughout day)
- Smaller visual weight than Steps

---

## 8. TabBar

**Component Name:** `TabBar`

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| activeTab | `'dashboard' \| 'log' \| 'overview'` | Yes | Currently active tab |
| onTabChange | (tab: string) => void | Yes | Tab change handler |

**Tab Config:**
| Tab ID | Label | Icon (Lucide) |
|--------|-------|---------------|
| dashboard | Dashboard | LayoutGrid |
| log | Log | PlusCircle |
| overview | Overview | BarChart3 |

**States:**
| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Default | Show all 3 tabs, active tab highlighted |

**Notes:**
- Fixed to bottom of screen
- Active: heavier icon stroke (2), semibold label, primary color
- Inactive: lighter stroke (1.5), regular weight, tertiary color
- Account for iOS safe area (`padding-bottom: env(safe-area-inset-bottom)`)

---

## 9. ProgressBar

**Component Name:** `ProgressBar`

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| value | number | Yes | â€” | Current value |
| max | number | Yes | â€” | Maximum/goal value |
| height | number | No | 12 | Height in pixels |
| variant | `'solid' \| 'gradient'` | No | 'gradient' | Fill style |

**States:**
| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Empty | Show track only |
| Partial | Show filled portion proportional to value/max |
| Full | Fill entire track (cap at 100%) |
| Loading | Pulsing animation on track |

**Notes:**
- No border radius (square ends)
- Solid variant: single `solidFill` color
- Gradient variant: Lâ†’R gradient

---

## 10. ProgressRing

**Component Name:** `ProgressRing`

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| value | number | Yes | â€” | Current value |
| max | number | Yes | â€” | Maximum/goal value |
| size | number | No | 130 | Diameter in pixels |
| strokeWidth | number | No | 12 | Ring thickness |
| children | ReactNode | No | â€” | Center content |

**States:**
| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Empty | Show track ring only |
| Partial | Fill arc proportional to value/max |
| Full | Complete ring (cap at 100%) |
| Loading | Pulsing animation |

**Notes:**
- Square ends (`strokeLinecap: butt`) â€” NOT rounded
- Rotation: starts at top (12 o'clock), fills clockwise
- Gradient applied to stroke

---

# ğŸ¥ˆ Design Tokens / Style Guide

```css
:root {
  /* ========== COLORS ========== */
  
  /* Backgrounds */
  --color-bg-primary: #FDF9F8;      /* App background */
  --color-bg-surface: #FFFFFF;      /* Cards, sections */
  --color-bg-accent: #FAF2EF;       /* Subtle highlights */
  
  /* Borders */
  --color-border-default: #F0E8E4;  /* Section dividers */
  
  /* Text */
  --color-text-primary: #3D352F;    /* Headlines, primary numbers */
  --color-text-secondary: #7A6E66;  /* Labels, row names */
  --color-text-tertiary: #A89E96;   /* Hints, goals, subtext */
  
  /* Progress */
  --color-progress-track: #F5EDEA;  /* Unfilled bar/ring */
  --color-progress-fill: #CBA090;   /* Solid bar fill */
  --color-gradient-start: #C9988A;  /* Gradient dark end */
  --color-gradient-end: #DBBEB4;    /* Gradient light end */
  
  /* Accent */
  --color-accent: #D9A090;          /* "X left", highlights */
  --color-accent-soft: #FAE8E2;     /* Badge backgrounds */
  
  /* Cycle Badge */
  --color-cycle-bg: #FAE8E2;
  --color-cycle-text: #C08A78;
  
  
  /* ========== TYPOGRAPHY ========== */
  
  /* Font Family */
  --font-family: "DM Sans", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
  
  /* Font Sizes */
  --font-size-display: 52px;        /* Sleep number */
  --font-size-headline: 44px;       /* Calorie number */
  --font-size-title: 28px;          /* Steps ring number */
  --font-size-large: 20px;          /* Sleep goal */
  --font-size-date: 18px;           /* Header date */
  --font-size-body: 16px;           /* Goal text, "X left" */
  --font-size-label: 15px;          /* Macro row labels */
  --font-size-small: 13px;          /* Badge text */
  --font-size-caption: 12px;        /* Section headers, subtext */
  --font-size-tiny: 11px;           /* Ring subtext */
  
  /* Font Weights */
  --font-weight-regular: 400;
  --font-weight-medium: 500;
  --font-weight-semibold: 600;
  --font-weight-bold: 700;
  
  /* Line Heights */
  --line-height-tight: 1;
  --line-height-normal: 1.4;
  
  
  /* ========== SPACING ========== */
  
  /* Base Unit */
  --space-unit: 8px;
  
  /* Section Padding */
  --section-padding-x: 24px;
  --section-padding-y: 20px;
  
  /* Component Spacing */
  --macro-row-gap: 18px;            /* Between macro rows */
  --label-gap: 8px;                 /* Label to bar */
  --ring-label-gap: 10px;           /* Ring to subtext */
  
  /* Progress Dimensions */
  --bar-height-large: 14px;         /* Calorie bar */
  --bar-height-default: 12px;       /* Macro bars */
  --ring-size: 130px;               /* Steps ring diameter */
  --ring-stroke: 12px;              /* Ring thickness */
  
  
  /* ========== BORDERS ========== */
  
  --border-radius: 0px;             /* Sharp corners (all elements) */
  --border-radius-badge: 24px;      /* Cycle badge only */
  --border-width: 1px;
  
  
  /* ========== TAB BAR ========== */
  
  --tab-bar-height: 70px;
  --tab-icon-size: 26px;
  --tab-label-size: 12px;
  
  
  /* ========== TRANSITIONS ========== */
  
  --transition-fast: 0.2s ease;
  --transition-default: 0.3s ease;
  --transition-slow: 0.5s ease;
}
```

