## Responsive Behavior

| Breakpoint | Width | Behavior |
|------------|-------|----------|
| Mobile (default) | < 768px | Full width, 24px side padding |
| Tablet | 768px - 1024px | Max-width 500px, centered |
| Desktop | > 1024px | Max-width 430px (iPhone width), centered |

**Target Device:** iPhone 17 Pro (430 x 932 logical points)

---

