# Quick Reference: Icon Library

Using **Lucide React** for all icons.

```bash
npm install lucide-react
```

| Icon | Import | Usage |
|------|--------|-------|
| Droplet | `import { Droplet } from 'lucide-react'` | Cycle badge |
| LayoutGrid | `import { LayoutGrid } from 'lucide-react'` | Dashboard tab |
| PlusCircle | `import { PlusCircle } from 'lucide-react'` | Log tab |
| BarChart3 | `import { BarChart3 } from 'lucide-react'` | Overview tab |

---

# Quick Reference: Font

**DM Sans** from Google Fonts

```html
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
```

Or in CSS:
```css
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
```

